{"tid":2252952,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國示威者前後夾擊包圍防暴警察 防暴被逼撒退","createTime":"2020-10-21T23:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T15:52:11.000Z","uid":278533,"like":55,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c56d7e027fe110c6d5dd66dfa2321d1e43247b1e","tid":2252952,"uid":278533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T23:43:06.000Z","msg":"竟然無人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪個個做番哂港豬睇CCTVB新聞  <br />\n <br />\n香港人講咗成年都做唔到既 泰國人幾日就完美示範<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n <br />\n前後夾攻 防暴防線被逼撒退 香港人遇到防線 只識開傘 正面硬碰 等人哋增援到 就迷戀RB 話夠安全，然後就變哂condom <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n人哋泰仔前面扮進攻 後面瞬間就殺出大量伏兵 將防暴完全包圍 被逼撒退 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n <br />\n戰術同團結完全表現出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n <br />\n香港呢 叫手足去後面反圍 得到嘅答覆係： 扮聽唔到   <br />\n <br />\n不了  你唔去  你係鬼  危險唔好  RB無人守  包到又點政府都唔會跪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc0cb7aed60dba2cff0098e50189a7de2273f0c","tid":2252952,"uid":278533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T23:46:48.000Z","msg":"cctvb唔敢播 想睇睇now新聞  <br />\n <br />\n有人討論再補片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed78402de7860437bc1e0948d3c39b394c9b97df","tid":2252952,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T23:47:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11a9b649f4